compat-change.description: Trying to read the wallpaper file or bitmap in T will return the default wallpaper bitmap/file instead of throwing a SecurityException.
compat-change.name: RETURN_DEFAULT_ON_SECURITY_EXCEPTION

compat-change.description: In U and later, attempting to read the wallpaper file or bitmap will throw an exception, (except with the READ_WALLPAPER_INTERNAL permission).
compat-change.name: THROW_ON_SECURITY_EXCEPTION
